trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The ManipulationDeltaEventArgs class contains data about changes in the position of a manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ManipulationDeltaEventArgs inneholder data om endringer i plasseringen av en redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.DeltaManipulation%2A> property contains the changes that occurred since the last <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta> event occurred.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.DeltaManipulation%2A>egenskapen inneholder endringer som oppstod etter siste <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta>oppstod.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.DeltaManipulation%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.CumulativeManipulation%2A> property contains the total changes that occurred for the current manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.CumulativeManipulation%2A>egenskapen inneholder de totale endringene som oppstod for gjeldende redigeringen.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.CumulativeManipulation%2A>

trans-unit.source: You use one of those properties to transform the manipulated object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke ett av disse egenskapene til transformeringen snytt objektet.

trans-unit.source: You can end a manipulation by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.Complete%2A> method or force the manipulation into inertia by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.StartInertia%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan avslutte en redigeringen ved å kalle den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.Complete%2A>metoden eller force redigeringen til treghet ved å kalle den <xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.StartInertia%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.StartInertia%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ManipulationDeltaEventArgs.Complete%2A>

trans-unit.source: Cancels the manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Avbryter redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: If the method succeeds, the default <xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice> sends previous touch events as mouse down or mouse move events to the element and future manipulation events do not occur.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden lykkes, standard <xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice>sender tidligere touch hendelser som musen eller mouse Flytt hendelser til elementet og fremtidige redigeringen hendelser skjer ikke.</xref:System.Windows.Input.TouchDevice>

trans-unit.source: Touch cannot be promoted to mouse events if the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted> event occurs during inertia.
trans-unit.target: Berøring kan ikke forfremmes til musen hendelser hvis den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted>inntreffer under treghet.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationCompleted>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the manipulation was successfully canceled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis redigeringen ble avbrutt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Completes the manipulation without inertia.
trans-unit.target: Fullfører redigeringen uten treghet.

trans-unit.source: You can call the Complete method to end the manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Du kan kalle metoden fullført for å avslutte redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: For example, when an object reaches the edge of a window, you can call Complete to prevent the object from going off the screen.
trans-unit.target: Når et objekt når kanten av et vindu, kan du for eksempel kalle Fullfør for å forhindre at objektet går ut av skjermen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the cumulated changes of the current manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Henter kumulerte endringene i gjeldende redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: The CumulativeManipulation property contains the total changes that occurred for the current manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CumulativeManipulation inneholder de totale endringene som oppstod for gjeldende redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: You can use CumulativeManipulation to transform the manipulated object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke CumulativeManipulation for transformeringen snytt objektet.

trans-unit.source: The cumulated changes of the current manipulation.
trans-unit.target: Gjeldende redigeringen kumulerte endringene.

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to transform the manipulated object.

trans-unit.target: De nyeste endringene i gjeldende redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"></xref> event occurs during inertia.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"> </xref> inntreffer under treghet.

trans-unit.source: You can use this method to determine whether the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta> event occurs during inertia or while the user has contact with the element that receives the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta> event.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne metoden til å bestemme om den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta>hendelsen oppstår under treghet eller når brukeren har kontakt med elementet mottar den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta>hendelsen.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"></xref> event occurs during inertia; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the event occurs while the user has contact with the <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationDelta"> </xref> inntreffer under treghet; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis hendelsen oppstår når brukeren har kontakt med den <xref href="System.Windows.UIElement"> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Henter beholderen som definerer koordinatene for redigeringen.

trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av objekter som representerer berøring kontaktene for redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: A collection of objects that represents the touch contacts for the manipulation.
trans-unit.target: En samling av objekter som representerer berøring kontaktene for redigeringen.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that the manipulation has gone beyond certain boundaries.
trans-unit.target: Angir at redigeringen er utenfor grensene enkelte.

trans-unit.source: Use the ReportBoundaryFeedback method to indicate that an element has moved beyond a certain boundary.
trans-unit.target: Bruk metoden ReportBoundaryFeedback for å angi at et element har flyttet forbi en bestemt grense.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a user moves an element outside of the bounds of a <xref:System.Windows.Window>, you can call this method to report that to the window.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en bruker flytter et element utenfor grensene for for eksempel en <xref:System.Windows.Window>, kan du kalle denne metoden hvis du vil rapportere som til vinduet.</xref:System.Windows.Window>

trans-unit.source: When you call ReportBoundaryFeedback, the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller ReportBoundaryFeedback, den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback>inntreffer.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback>

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Windows.Window> subscribes to the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback> event to provide visual feedback to the user that a boundary has been reached.
trans-unit.target: Som standard i <xref:System.Windows.Window>abonnerer på den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback>hendelse som visual tilbakemelding til brukeren som en grense er nådd.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback> </xref:System.Windows.Window>

trans-unit.source: You can subscribe to <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback> to implement custom behavior.
trans-unit.target: Du kan abonnere på <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback>implementere egendefinerte virkemåte.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.ManipulationBoundaryFeedback>

trans-unit.source: The portion of the manipulation that represents moving beyond the boundary.
trans-unit.target: Delen av redigeringen som representerer å øke grensen.
